  "analysis_steps": [
    "Step 1: Identified daily bullish bias and daily profile showing Asia high as key draw-on liquidity, with London consolidation below it.",
    "Step 2: Observed London session sweeping the prior low (turtle soup/purge), triggering liquidity and setting up reversal conditions.",
