    "Step 5: Recognized confluence of breaker block and new FVG forming at the reaction zone, supporting continuation higher toward Asia highs.",
    "Step 6: Simplified focus to change in state of delivery and order block mean threshold for entry, avoiding over-analysis of all PD arrays."
